summary: This is not a mod, this is pack with about 15 mods in it.
descriptionHtml: This mod pack contains: Apachii hair males/females, Better cities more art, No spinning death animation, Dwarf race and followers, Maximum Drive, Playable giant race, Riverwood reborn, Samurai Blades and kimono, Superjump 2x (back flip jump), snow instead of fog in main menu, different background in main menu, music theme Dragonborn Comes by Jeff Winner, Kick bash, new animation with one handed and magic, Buster sward one and two handed from FF7, Sorrow Katanas and some more mods.
author: Lejsmo
